<h3>
	Eames Lounge Chair and Ottoman by Herman Miller&nbsp;
</h3>
<p>
	这是由纽约街头品牌 3sixteen 和家具品牌 Herman Miller 联手推出的躺椅，设计源自用久了棒球手套，有深浅两种颜色和自然的褶皱，里面的天然植物鞣皮会随着时间变暗，外面一层是木板，涂上了古铜色的木油，与浅色皮革正好是两个方向的纹路，<span>很有年代感。目前</span>只制作了三张限量发售。
</p>
<p>
</p>
<p style="text-align:center;">
	<img src="/uploads/image/201512/dafc8165bd07.jpg" width="1080" height="720" title=" " alt=" " /><span> </span> 
</p>
<p style="text-align:center;">
	<img src="/uploads/image/201512/e1255b90e11f.jpg" width="1080" height="720" title=" " alt=" " /><span> </span> 
</p>
<p style="text-align:center;">
	<img src="/uploads/image/201512/e55d51e163a7.jpg" width="1080" height="720" title=" " alt=" " /><span> </span> 
</p>
<p style="text-align:center;">
	<img src="/uploads/image/201512/6a4fa91d72e8.jpg" width="1080" height="720" title=" " alt=" " /><span> </span> 
</p>
<p style="text-align:center;">
	<img src="/uploads/image/201512/36cea7c4c731.jpg" width="1080" height="720" title=" " alt=" " /> 
</p>
<p>
</p>
<h3>
	SHINOLA + WORKOF HOLIDAY ORNAMENT AUCTION
</h3>
<p>
	34&nbsp;家来自纽约或洛杉矶的设计事务所为 MOCAD（Museum of Contemporary Art Detroit，底特律现代美术馆）设计了这些节日的装点。有带彩色纹理的石头、蓝色的气球、金属框、挂起来的盆景，总之每家事务所使用了不同的材料或元素，也以此代表自己的理念，比普通的装饰物多了一份艺术感，很适合挂在圣诞树上。<a href="http://paddle8.com/auction/shinolaworkof/" target="_blank">点击这里可以查看更多信息。</a> 
</p>
<p>
</p>
<p style="text-align:center;">
	<img src="/uploads/image/201512/e0af918eb737.jpg" width="1080" height="720" title=" " alt=" " /><span> </span> 
</p>
<p style="text-align:center;">
	<img src="/uploads/image/201512/b05ad3d47a53.jpg" width="600" height="400" title=" " alt=" " /><span> </span> 
</p>
<p style="text-align:center;">
	<img src="/uploads/image/201512/afffb87425bd.jpg" width="600" height="400" title=" " alt=" " /><span> </span> 
</p>
<p style="text-align:center;">
	<img src="/uploads/image/201512/1f8e8efc1c79.jpg" width="600" height="400" title=" " alt=" " /><span> </span> 
</p>
<p style="text-align:center;">
	<img src="/uploads/image/201512/60dfb58d826e.jpg" width="600" height="400" title=" " alt=" " /><span> </span> 
</p>
<p style="text-align:center;">
	<img src="/uploads/image/201512/1735bb961f76.jpg" width="600" height="400" title=" " alt=" " /> 
</p>
<p>
</p>
<h3>
	HeLi-on by infinityPV
</h3>
<p>
	这是丹麦的设计公司&nbsp;infinityPV&nbsp;研发出来的太阳能充电器，从充电器中间可以展开一张超薄的太阳能面板，然后放在阳光下蓄电。蓄电之后直接收回在&nbsp;11.3&nbsp;厘米长的容器中，方便携带。这款充电器可以储存&nbsp;2600mAh&nbsp;的电量，可与手机、移动电源等设备相连。产品目前正在众筹，<a href="http://www.kickstarter.com/projects/infinitypv/heli-on?ref=nav_search" target="_blank">这里是众筹链接。</a> 
</p>
<p>
</p>
<p style="text-align:center;">
	<img src="/uploads/image/201512/746dfc58e86b.jpg" width="818" height="545" title=" " alt=" " /><span> </span> 
</p>
<p style="text-align:center;">
	<img src="/uploads/image/201512/a57e2cae2ff7.jpg" width="818" height="545" title=" " alt=" " /><span> </span> 
</p>
<p style="text-align:center;">
	<img src="/uploads/image/201512/d83415414fde.jpg" width="818" height="545" title=" " alt=" " /><span> </span> 
</p>
<p style="text-align:center;">
	<img src="/uploads/image/201512/fe5057a86f82.jpg" width="818" height="614" title=" " alt=" " /><span> </span> 
</p>
<p style="text-align:center;">
	<img src="/uploads/image/201512/7fd7c38beb9e.jpg" width="818" height="580" title=" " alt=" " /><span> </span> 
</p>
<p>
</p>
<h3>
	Star Wars Planetary Glassware Set
</h3>
<p>
	这是一组非常绚丽的玻璃杯，将《星际大战》中的行星图案印到了上面，一共&nbsp;6&nbsp;个，包括&nbsp;4个行星、月球和死星。每个杯子都呈现出复杂细密的纹路，依托着球形的杯体，让杯子本身成为一个小的星球，是收藏癖的专爱。另有太阳系各星球图案，每个售价&nbsp;50&nbsp;美元，<a href="http://www.thinkgeek.com/product/irkr/?cpg=cj&ref=&CJURL=&AID=10746449&PID=7817402&SID=skim82526X1534134Xa5e6db398f4de21aca27ca7867f240f9&CJID=2617611" target="_blank">这里是购买链接。</a> 
</p>
<p>
</p>
<p style="text-align:center;">
	<img src="/uploads/image/201512/4b8ddf1722a3.jpg" width="600" height="542" title=" " alt=" " /><span> </span> 
</p>
<p style="text-align:center;">
	<img src="/uploads/image/201512/51d74494a804.jpg" width="600" height="498" title=" " alt=" " /><span> </span> 
</p>
<p style="text-align:center;">
	<img src="/uploads/image/201512/023516d90b93.jpg" width="600" height="485" title=" " alt=" " /><span> </span> 
</p>
<p style="text-align:center;">
	<img src="/uploads/image/201512/518abd466ece.jpg" width="600" height="600" title=" " alt=" " /><span> </span> 
</p>
<p style="text-align:center;">
	<img src="/uploads/image/201512/8bc4b82f939c.jpg" width="600" height="600" title=" " alt=" " /> 
</p>
<p>
</p>
<h3>
	BONNIE &amp; CLYDE by Pearly Yon
</h3>
<p>
	这组&nbsp;gin&nbsp;的包装是以&nbsp;Bonny and Clyde（雌雄大盗）为灵感的，甜一些的是&nbsp;Bonnie，烈一些的是&nbsp;Clyde。瓶身已经接近长方形了，上面描绘的文字和图案都有&nbsp;20&nbsp;世纪早期的广告画风格，像是带有装饰性的海报。设计师&nbsp;Pearly Yon&nbsp;以这两人的和谐关系来象征这两瓶酒的互补和持久。
</p>
<p>
</p>
<p style="text-align:center;">
	<img src="/uploads/image/201512/527cc7670f2b.jpg" width="1080" height="1080" title=" " alt=" " /><span> </span> 
</p>
<p style="text-align:center;">
	<img src="/uploads/image/201512/6310be080b56.jpg" width="1080" height="1080" title=" " alt=" " /><span> </span> 
</p>
<p style="text-align:center;">
	<img src="/uploads/image/201512/4ba5fd49a19c.jpg" width="1080" height="1080" title=" " alt=" " /><span> </span> 
</p>
<p style="text-align:center;">
	<img src="/uploads/image/201512/bed0b1564096.jpg" width="1080" height="886" title=" " alt=" " /><span> </span> 
</p>
<p style="text-align:center;">
	<img src="/uploads/image/201512/4540423c67ba.jpg" width="1080" height="886" title=" " alt=" " /> 
</p>
